Company Info: Summit Systems
Welcome to Summit Systems, a global tech company that builds smart tools for modern businesses. In this simulation, you’ll step into the role of a Business Operations Associate, handling real-world workplace scenarios through email.

Who We Are
Summit Systems helps companies run smoother with powerful automation and clean design. We value integrity, teamwork, adaptability, and customer-first thinking.

How the Inbox Game Works
You’ll receive emails from coworkers, clients, and managers. For each message, choose the best response from the options provided.

Your decisions will be graded based on:

Communication clarity

Task prioritization

Professional tone

Alignment with company values

